<div class="blog" >

  <div class="grid" id="bloggrid">

    <div class="grid-item grid-item--achievments stamp stamp1">
  <a href="/"><div class="grid-item-content">
  </div></a>
</div>

    <div class="grid-item grid-item--contactinfo stamp stamp2">
      <div class="grid-item-content">
        <p>
          Normally, both your asses would be dead as fucking fried chicken, but you happen to pull this shit while I'm in a transitional period so I don't wanna kill you, I wanna help you. But I can't give you this case, it don't belong to me. Besides, I've
